We could have stayed at a much nicer hotel for the price, but since it was non-refundable, we continued to stay there.	I would definately recommend the Murray Hill East and wouldn't hesitate to stay there in the future.	We would deffinately stay here again, everyone was very nice and the location was worth it for what we got in our room just for being a little outside of Times Square.	We have stayed elsewhere, but nowhere else is as good and we will always stay here is there are rooms available.	I think it would not be a good place to stay if you are there on business.